ICH10 LPC Bridge Test Description
=================================

Included Cases
--------------
The ICH10 LPC bridge test totally includes 4 cases:
(1) s-fwhi-connect.py: tests firmware hub to connect external devices 
(2) s-fwhi-boot.py: tests firmware hub to connect and read data from legacy flash
(3) s-lpc-bridge.py: tests the bridge function between PCI and LPC bus of LPC bridge
(4) s-serial-ports.py: tests LPC bridge can connect up to 4 RS232 controllers.



Not Tested Features
-------------------
(1) The PCI interrupt routing registers in LPC bridge are not tested.
